name: LOGO DESIGN
description:
Want a new logo for your new or existing company? All you need to do is just to fill in one of our questionnaires and we will sort out the rest for you. Service includes 3 logo drafts of your interest, up to 5 times modification, and completed logo in different file format and sizes for your convenience. 
Once the logo is made and decided for you we will not resell it to other person(s)/ companies.

Promotion : A free single sided business card design upon request. (Please note that at the moment you will need to source for you printing company.)

Thank you

name: POSTER DESIGN
description:
All you need to do is provide us 
1. Information which you would like to put on the poster
2. Image(s) if there is any
3. The final size you want your file to be in
4. And of course, let us know how you want it to be if you want us to execute your idea.

And...
1. We send 3 proposals on posters layout/suggestion.
2. You decide and we execute. 
3. Up to 5 times amendments. (So please send as many information as possible at once =) )

We can also
1. Do photo montage/ color adjustment if you need
2. trace a logo if there is a need
3. send you posters files of a same design in any format and size you need.

Please do not hesitate to contact us if there is any questions.

name: PHOTO EDITING BOOTH
description:
We provide photo editing service for only 30p/photo. 
1. You send us photo(s) that you wish to edit.
2. We will email you to let you know if the photo is editable, you can also let us know how you would like it to be.
3. We will send you the edited photo adjusted to the size you want.

Photo editing service includes 
1. red eye fixing
2. skin texture fixing (ie. fine lines/spots/freckles)
3. underexposed picture
4. overexposed( in this case please seek advice before purchase as some overexposed photos are not possible to fix)
5. color adjustment/contrast adjustment
6. photo enhancement ( to make the "object" out-stand the background.
7. face/body shape correction. (ie. to get rid of double chin, cellulite, etc, anything that you can think of =) ) 
8. add words to your photos

Photo montage:
If photo montage is requested, it will be charged differently. If it is requested to merge 3 photos in any way ( could be taking some part of a photo and put it in another), then it will be charged as 3x0.30p=90p.

Time estimation:
If it is less than 10 photos to be edited---> within 24 hours
if it is more than 10, less than 30 photos--> 48 hours
We will quote a time for you if we think that the photo require more time to be edited.
 
We will adjust every photo to your satisfaction. Or you can have your money back =)
